@thekerrypowell Chatted with @ameliacostello3 and think we might have a good work around.

Could we impose a rule that someone who signs into the Proposal page and is a secondary contact, we throw a pop-up over the page that asks them to confirm they have checked with the primary contact that they haven’t already started filling out the renewal proposal?

That way we don’t have to write complicated system updates to actually stop it from happening, we just put another opportunity for it to not happen.
